LRGs: lrgdbconsax5db.
Suites: (none).
Description: tsagx5config.tsc - Configures an X5 system using DEBUGCLI

Two types of X5 systems can be set
    1) High Capacity - 12 HDs and 4 NVMe devices
    let x5_hc_setup true (Required, and is also default)
          let nvme_size <size in MB>  (optional, takes 512M as default)

    2) All Flash - 8 or 12 NVMe devices
          let x5_af_setup true (Required)
          let nvme_size <size in MB> (optional, takes 512M as default)
          let num_af_dev <8 or 12>   (default is 8 devices)

To use this script, include it in the beginning of the test after setting
     up required variables (as described above) for the desired setup
